author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
Welcome everyone to your weekly escape from the ennui of modern living; the GMG Monday Show. This is our monthy free episode where we hang out, catch up on the news of the week and what we've been hobbying on and get ready to brave the ordeals to come. 

MAILBAG for Patrons is at the usual link!
title: The Monday Show FREEPISODE - Is GW finally taking the RIGHT lessons from the Video Game industry?

author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
Welcome back to TACTICAL AWARENESS - a Canadian Podcast about Corvus Belli’s landmark Sci-Fi Wargame; Infinity N5. Come along with our hosts Ash, Owen and Dan for a whole new ITS Edition of Infinity! 

It's the newest Sectorial from Yu Jing today; the White Banner! Launched with the WinterFor in Operation: Kaldstrom this faction blends elements of all the previous sectorials with the Sneakiness of lots of Albedo and Melee!
